Package: DUET
Title: FDR-Controlled Feature Selection from Paired 16S and Shotgun Microbiome Count Data
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yuxuan", "Du", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "yuxuan.du@utsa.edu"),
    person("Yiqiao", "Zhu", role = "aut"))
Description: DUET implements a knockoff-based framework for integrative feature selection from paired 16S and shotgun microbiome count data. DUET tests, for each taxon, a union null that it is not conditionally associated with the outcome in at least one platform, so discoveries reflect associations replicated across both technologies.
